---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="DEMWeb Studio is a solo web design and SEO studio building fast, honest websites for small businesses and freelancers."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-24 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl">About DEMWeb Studio</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg text-ink-secondary">
      <p>
        DEMWeb Studio is a solo web design and SEO studio. It exists because too many small businesses and
        freelancers end up with a website that's either slow, hard to find in search, or both — usually because it
        was built from a generic template with more features than the business ever needed, and less performance
        than it deserved.
      </p>
      <p>
        The studio is built around a narrower focus: fast, hand-built websites with SEO treated as part of the
        build, not an afterthought bolted on later. That means static-first tooling, self-hosted fonts, clean
        markup, and no unnecessary third-party scripts slowing pages down — the same standard this site is held to.
      </p>
      <p>
        Clients are typically small companies and independent freelancers who need a site that actually represents
        the business and gets found in search — not an agency-scale engagement with agency-scale overhead.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border border-border bg-card p-8 sm:p-10">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-medium text-ink">How projects run</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-ink-secondary">
        Every project follows the same five-step process, from first conversation to post-launch support.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/process"
        class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-sm font-medium text-teal hover:underline"
      >
        See how we work →
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-start gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
      <p class="text-ink-secondary">Have a project in mind?</p>
      <Button href="/contact">Get a Free Quote</Button>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
